计\n6. 新增筹码特征（turnover_rate/volume_up）：量能变化\n7. 升级双模型：XGBoost + LightGBM 融合\n8. 5折时序交叉验证替代简单训练/测试分割\n\n## 下一步计划\n1. 引入真实竞价数据（quicktiny auction接口），替代当前代理特征\n2. 尝试 CatBoost 或 RandomForest 进一步融合\n3. 加入北向资金/融资融券等另类数据\n4. 调优 LightGBM 融合权重（目前等权平均）\n5. 针对退潮期/冰点期单独建模"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":40250,"output":905,"cacheRead":25966,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67121,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774285083321}}
