{"type":"message","id":"968021c1","parentId":"4b37b315","timestamp":"2026-03-23T16:58:26.276Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The report has been sent successfully. Let me provide a summary of what was accomplished.","thinkingSignature":"bb01f6a6224451318ecda8c3a1dd1a502b5b9001ab47ea41e86d7076391c70a8"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n## 任务完成\n\nA股超短模型训练 v2 已成功执行，结果如下：\n\n**核心成果：**\n- AUC 从 0.6097 → 0.7534（测试集），提升 **+14.37%**\n- 5折时序交叉验证 AUC 均值 **0.7871 ± 0.0681**\n- 新增 16 个特征（26 个特征总数）\n- 双模型（XGBoost + LightGBM）已保存到 `data/astock/model/`\n\n**最重要发现：**\n市场情绪类特征（market_temperature + zbgc_rate + rise_fall_ratio）是最强预测因子，合计贡献 48% 的特征重要性，远超原有技术指标。\n\n**报告已发送到飞书**（messageId: om_x100b53235c66c0a0c458b0a5a658e90）\n\n**模型文件：**\n- `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/data/astock/model/xgb_model_v2.pkl`\n- `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/data/astock/model/lgb_model_v2.pkl`\n- `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/data/astock/model/model_metadata_v2.json`\n\n**注意：** 竞价特征（auction_chng 等）使用了 `jb_prob/adj_factor` 作为代理，因为 quicktiny 历史竞价接口无法批量获取。未来接入真实竞价数据后，模型性能有望进一步提升。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41230,"output":332,"cacheRead":25966,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67528,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774285099012}}
